Ranger Help for: concealment
=============================

SYNTAX:      conceal
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             underground,mountain,arctic,barren
SLOT COST:   8
BASE SP:     25
SKILL TYPE:  stealth

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to hide using natural camouflage, blending
into the surrounding terrain. The Ranger must not be in combat to use
this skill. While concealed, the Ranger is invisible to most creatures
and players. Moving or initiating combat will break the concealment.
Concealment is a prerequisite for the ambush skill. The effectiveness
depends on the Ranger's dexterity, skill level, and the type of
terrain. Some terrains offer better natural cover than others.
